{"tid":276141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長洲東堤小築男女燒炭亡 雙方各有家室","createTime":"2017-06-08T14:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T14:40:29.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df8d729f4e902790f4fd1e523f54a9f0b736b5e3","tid":276141,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T14:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/5ey_i.uyn0t3rcnlBEO.rQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170608a151518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5ey_i.uyn0t3rcnlBEO.rQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170608a151518.jpg&h=debc461e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】長洲東堤小築渡假屋負責人下午約2時30分，發現一男一女租客遲遲未退房，故到渡假屋查看，發現大門反鎖，心感不妙於是報警處理。消防到場破門入屋，發現一男一女倒卧單位內，當場證實死亡，警方正封鎖現場展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，兩名死者年約40歲，單位內發現有多個酒樽。事發現場為東堤小築一個地下豪華海景套房。雙方各有家室，女死者丈夫到認屍後傷心痛哭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E6%B4%B2%E6%9D%B1%E5%A0%A4%E5%B0%8F%E7%AF%89%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E7%87%92%E7%82%AD%E4%BA%A1-%E9%9B%99%E6%96%B9%E5%90%84%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%A4-102500199.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%25A0%25A4%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25AF%2589%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2587%2592%25E7%2582%25AD%25E4%25BA%25A1-%25E9%259B%2599%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2590%2584%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25AE%25A4-102500199.html&d=iOPvj4WU1MgCj6%2FE9Hyrgf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6261d0bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%95%B7%E6%B4%B2%E6%9D%B1%E5%A0%A4%E5%B0%8F%E7%AF%89%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E7%87%92%E7%82%AD%E4%BA%A1-%E9%9B%99%E6%96%B9%E5%90%84%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%A4-102500199.html</a>"}]}